Class MenuConstants

java.lang.Object
constant.MenuConstants
public final class MenuConstants extends Object
Constants for menu choices, field indices, and table navigation. Centralizes all UI command strings and index values.
Since:
2025-11-16
Version:
1.0
Author:
NTU SC2002 Group
